{"word":"G1756 - ἐνεργής - energḗs - en-er-gace' - Effectual","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνεργής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">energḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-er-gace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Effectual</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அநுகூலமான, பயனுள்ள, வல்லமையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"effectual, powerful, active, operative"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G2041 - ἔργον - érgon - er'-gon/2041\">G2041</a>; <i>active</i>, <i>operative:</i> - effectual, powerful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1753/1753\">G1753</a>, <a href=\"#/G1754/1754\">G1754</a>, <a href=\"#/G1755/1755\">G1755</a>, <a href=\"#/G1756/1756\">G1756</a>, <a href=\"#/G2038/2038\">G2038</a>, <a href=\"#/G2039/2039\">G2039</a>, <a href=\"#/G2040/2040\">G2040</a>, <a href=\"#/G2041/2041\">G2041</a>, <a href=\"#/G2108/2108\">G2108</a>, <a href=\"#/G2109/2109\">G2109</a>, <a href=\"#/G2110/2110\">G2110</a>"}]}